description.@value: グリュンヴェーデルの晩年の活動期に属する研究書。トルキスタンの石窟は、純粋なタントラの伝統に基づくものではなく、オリエントの悪魔図像の系統を引く、特に悪魔的な要素においてマニ教とエトルスクの関係が深いものであると述べる。400冊限定出版の46番。

A study written by Grünwedel in later years of his career. Grünwedel considered that the grottos in Turkistan were not based on the pure tradition of Tantra but was descended from the Oriental Satanic iconology and had close relationship with Manichaeism and Etrusk. Number 46 out of 400 limited publications.
